name: Inner Self (Primo Adrian)
description:
This is my first completed game 

"EAZY MODE" takes 2 minutes to complete

"PLAY" mode takes 5 minutes to complete

My highest score is 27.620 if I remember correctly - try and beat it - also, enjoy!

Edit: I actually tried a bit harder and got to 29.090 score and I have the picture to prove it =)) (the 3rd screenshot)

More games at later dates! Also, "Music?" is supposed to be a joke, since I am not yet good at making music. xD (it will also reset to default "0%" volume after a round in case you actually wanted to play with it on and you will need to switch it back up)
